 <h2>Mall Services</h2>
<p>Located on the Lower Level across From La Senza,&nbsp;Halifax Shopping Centre’s Customer Service Centre, along with our amenities, can make your shopping easier!</p>
<ul>
<li>Free Wifi &ndash; NEW!</li>
<li>Complimentary coat /parcel check</li>
<li>Seasonal gift wrapping services</li>
<li><a href="/gift_cards">Halifax Shopping Centre Gift Cards</a></li>
<li>Wheelchair Loans</li>
<li>Stroller loan program</li>
<li>Family Parking spots at each entrance</li>
<li>Baby care rooms on each level</li>
<li>Mall maps and store listings</li>
<li>Metro Transit Terminal and Yellow Cab service on-site</li>
<li>Lost &amp; Found</li>
<li>Mall Paging</li>
<li>Tourism Information</li>
<li>Postal services available in Lawton’s Drug Store</li>
<li>Battery boost and lost vehicle search</li>
<li>24 hour on-site security with Close circuit Television surveillance, crime prevention and intervention and emergency medical assistance</li>
</ul>
<h5>Kiddie Kabs</h5>
<p>With a $2 donation to local children’s charities you may utilise a Kiddie Kab during mall hours while visiting Halifax Shopping Centre. Our&nbsp;Kiddie Kab and strollers&nbsp;services are offered as a convenience when the equipment&nbsp;is available, and&nbsp;are subject to height&nbsp; restrictions as imposed by&nbsp;the equipment manufacturer’s specifications, to ensure the safety of your child.</p>
<h5>Questions?</h5>
<p><strong>Customer Service:</strong>&nbsp;(902) 453-1752</p>
<p>Our Customer Service staff are World Host certified and dedicated to continuing to raise the bar of service excellence.</p>
